languageToKeyword: {en=[mountain, highest after, Annapurna], de=[Berg, höchster nach, Annapurna], es=[montaña, más alta después de, Annapurna], it=[montagna, più alta dopo, Annapurna], fr=[montagne, la plus haute, Annapurna], nl=[berg, hoogste na, Annapurna]}
sparqlQuery:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri
WHERE {       
        res:Annapurna dbo:elevation ?elevation .
        ?uri rdf:type dbo:Mountain . 
        ?uri dbo:elevation ?otherelevation .
        FILTER (?otherelevation < ?elevation) .
} 
ORDER BY DESC(?otherelevation) LIMIT 1

sparqlQuery:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

}

languageToKeyword: {en=[bridge, same type, Manhattan Bridge], de=[Brücke, gleicher Typ, Manhattan Bridge], es=[puente, mismo tipo, puente de Manhattan], it=[ponte, stesso tipo, ponte di Manhattan], fr=[ponts, même type, pont de Manhattan], nl=[brug, zelfde type, Manhattan Bridge]}
sparqlQuery:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri 
WHERE {       
        ?uri rdf:type dbo:Bridge .
        ?uri dbp:design ?design .
        res:Manhattan_Bridge dbp:design ?mdesign . 
        FILTER (regex(?design, ?mdesign)).
        FILTER (?uri != res:Manhattan_Bridge) . 
}
